    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Free, Professional, Starter (legacy) and Team (legacy) plans, Global Rulesets`}</strong>{`: You will find this key under `}<strong parentName="p">{`Services`}</strong>{` :fa-arrow-right: `}<strong parentName="p">{`Event Rules`}</strong>{` and it will be listed under `}<strong parentName="p">{`Incoming Event Source`}</strong>{`. `}</p>
    <p><strong parentName="p">{`Business and Global Operations plans, Global Rulesets`}</strong>{`: You will find this key under `}<strong parentName="p">{`Services`}</strong>{` :fa-arrow-right: `}<strong parentName="p">{`Event Rules`}</strong>{` :fa-arrow-right: click your desired ruleset `}<strong parentName="p">{`name`}</strong>{` and it will be listed under `}<strong parentName="p">{`Incoming Event Source`}</strong>{`. `}</p>
    <p>{`If you are sending events through the Events API, use this integration key in the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`service_key`}</inlineCode>{` field (`}<a parentName="p" {...{
